item.title: CVE-2021-38175|2024-08-04T01:37:16.309Z -- sap%20se -- sap%20analysis%20for%20microsoft%20office
item.description: SAP Analysis for Microsoft Office - version 2.8, allows an attacker with high privileges to read sensitive data over the network, and gather or change information in the current system without user interaction. The attack would not lead to an impact on the availability of the system, but there would be an impact on integrity and confidentiality.
